      <description>&lt;section class=&#34;py-16 bg-gradient-to-b from-purple-50 to-white&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;container mx-auto px-4&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;        &#xD;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;max-w-6xl mx-auto text-center&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;        &lt;h1 class=&#34;text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6 text-gray-900&#34;&gt;Our Research Areas&lt;/h1&gt;&#xD;&#xA;        &lt;p class=&#34;text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;            We conduct cutting-edge interdisciplinary research at the intersection of population dynamics, public health, and social policy to address the most pressing challenges of our time&#xD;&#xA;        &lt;/p&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;/section&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;section class=&#34;py-16&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;container mx-auto px-4&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;        &#xD;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;max-w-6xl mx-auto&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;        &lt;!-- Work and Employment --&gt;&#xD;&#xA;        &lt;div class=&#34;mb-16&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;            &lt;div class=&#34;bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg overflow-hidden&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;                &lt;div class=&#34;bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500 to-blue-600 p-8&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;                    &lt;h2 class=&#34;text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-2&#34;&gt;Work and Employment&lt;/h2&gt;&#xD;&#xA;                    &lt;p class=&#34;text-blue-100&#34;&gt;Examining the changing nature of work and its impact on wellbeing&lt;/p&gt;</description>
